text: Here at Ngee Ann Polytechnic School of Design and Environment ground floor atrium you can find the public piano which is decently playable.
Open place to cry about your projects. Stream Lana  Del Rey or Twice for tough days
Always end up here for lecture, classrooms quite nice.

author_name: 妹兄日记 真心诚意好华为荣耀一飞冲天
